## Sleepwell (Next.js) – environment variables
## Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in values.
##
## IMPORTANT:
## - `.env.local` is gitignored by design (see `.gitignore`)
## - These are PUBLIC keys intended for client-side usage.

NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL="https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co"
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY="YOUR_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY"

## Debug: set to "1" to disable Supabase Realtime (helps isolate write issues)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_DISABLE_SUPABASE_REALTIME="1"

